The paper discusses machine learning theory and practice, specifically focusing on the design of Gaussian Processes and the convergence analysis of deep neural nets. It also discusses the behavior of neural networks under stochastic gradient descent and the Neural Tangent Kernel. These topics are all closely related to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and control systems (cs.SY).
